high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap to the right of the sink.
Walk over to the tub.
Put the car of soap in the tub in front of the rag.
Turn around and walk to the drawers to the left of the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap on the right edge of the top of the drawers.
Turn right and walk back over to the tub.
Put the bar of soap in the tub to the right of the other bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the tub.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the tub.
Put the bar of soap into the tub.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn right to face the cabinet.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the cabinet.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the tub.
Put the bar of soap into the tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap into the tub.

high_descs: Turn around, walk forward to the bar of soap by the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the bath tub basin.
Turn around, walk forward to the door, then turn right towards the bars of soap near the tissue boxes.
Pick up the bar of soap on the right.
Turn right and walk back to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the bath tub basin, to the right of the first bar.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap in a bath tub.
